1
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,570
Why are you still following me?

2
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,240
Stop pretending, Brother Qingxuan.

3
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,200
This road leads to Tushan.

4
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,320
What?

5
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,290
Afraid we'll hold you back?

6
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,360
Are you sure you want to follow me to die?

7
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,280
Ancestor,

8
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,440
you are mistaken.

9
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,880
We are not going to slaughter demons this time,

10
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,160
but to save someone.

11
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,600
Besides, with the two of us here,

12
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,480
our chances of winning should be higher.

13
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,960
We at Sitiantai are demon hunters.

14
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:39,560
We don't need to report to you about going to Tushan, do we?

15
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,000
My immortal body is damaged now.

16
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,570
I'm afraid I can't protect you.

17
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,170
If anything goes wrong,

18
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,640
at best, you'll lose a thousand years of cultivation.

19
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,480
At worst, your core and spirit will be destroyed,

20
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,480
never to recover.

21
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,480
As for you,

22
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,140
once you lose your life...

23
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:03,330
Then you'll have nothing left.

24
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,800
Don't worry.

25
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,800
I will bear

26
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,420
all the consequences.

27
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,640
Me too.

28
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:50,810
Hyah!

29
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,440
What is this?

30
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,680
What thing?

31
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:32,060
The Golden Immortal's disciple.

32
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,020
His aptitude is ordinary.

33
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,480
He is nothing special.

34
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,900
Will the Golden Immortal come to Tushan for him?

35
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,860
Your Highness.

36
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:43,280
The Golden Immortal has people from the Sitian Bureau by his side.

37
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,840
It is truly difficult to deal with.

38
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:47,280
So we can only start with his disciple.

39
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,060
Please calm down, Your Highness.

40
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,000
How can I calm down?

41
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,400
I cut off the Golden Immortal's immortal root.

42
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,330
He will definitely not let this go.

43
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,460
Rest assured, Your Highness.

44
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,080
We will wait for him for three days.

45
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,140
If he doesn't come,

46
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:09,210
I will go meet him again.

47
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,690
Thank you for sparing my life, My Lady.

48
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:33,440
Since you were capable enough to sever his immortal root,

49
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,700
why didn't you bring him back as well?

50
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,659
In the Upper Realm,

51
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,060
I am on par with the Hong Sword.

52
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:43,000
There is a world of difference between me and a Golden Immortal.

53
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:46,360
Qingxuan achieved godhood in a single thought after hundreds of thousands of years.

54
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,880
Though he is merely a gatekeeper of Sanshanliu,

55
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,960
his combat power

56
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,010
and cultivation

57
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,520
are above all minor gods.

58
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,970
Severing his immortal root

59
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,040
was just a desperate act of quick thinking.

60
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,040
Whether it was severed completely

61
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,170
is still uncertain.

62
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,560
And even if his immortal body is sealed,

63
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,810
I can't be sure I can defeat him.

64
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,600
In that case,

65
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,100
I will wait for him for three days.

66
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,640
If he doesn't come,

67
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,440
I will go in person.

68
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,040
Li,

69
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,440
you must remember,

70
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,760
you are now Jinwang.

71
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:31,290
You are no longer an ancient artifact of the Heavenly Realm.

72
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:35,200
You cannot escape my grasp.

73
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,570
I would not dare.

74
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:44,440
Take this little thing down and look after it well.

75
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,220
Don't let it get eaten.

76
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,320
I'm so hungry.

77
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,640
I left in such a hurry.

78
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,640
I didn't bring any food.

79
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,540
Who told you not to bring food?

80
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,480
What were you doing earlier?

81
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,540
Then I'll help myself.

82
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,880
If only Feilu were here.

83
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:43,760
His roasted rabbit is so delicious.

84
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,280
Ancestor,

85
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,400
that Jinwang,

86
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,650
you know him?

87
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,250
He held a post in heaven.

88
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,530
Why did he come down to be a monster?

89
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,560
I'm not trying to pry into your past.

90
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,280
I just think

91
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,000
if we know our enemy and know ourselves,

92
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,600
it's better to have some understanding of him.

93
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,240
After all,

94
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,880
what happened in Ercheng

95
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,600
is too bizarre.

96
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,160
He is not a deity,

97
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,260
and has no divine post.

98
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,200
He is a weapon,

99
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,160
an ancient divine artifact.

100
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,400
A divine artifact.

101
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,560
In ancient times,

102
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,600
the four pillars collapsed,

103
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,000
and the sky couldn't cover the earth.

104
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,530
The high goddess Nuwa mended the sky with five-colored stones.

105
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:39,080
The remaining stones were scattered across the nine provinces.

106
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,140
Two of them are in the immortal realm,

107
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:44,410
refined by the spiritual spring of Mount Sumeru,

108
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:47,100
resulting in two weapons with divine power.

109
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,040
One is my sword,

110
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,880
named Hong.

111
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,810
It stays with me in the Sanshan Sect

112
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:04,240
and can sever the emotions of those turning immortal.

113
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,280
The other one,

114
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,480
in the Guixu Mirror of the Wangchuan River,

115
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,440
named Li,

116
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:10,760
can sever the immortal roots of deities falling to the mortal realm.

117
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,840
He is like Hong,

118
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,610
but also different.

119
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:15,600
He has divine consciousness

120
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,600
and a human form.

121
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,360
Severing immortal roots for a long time

122
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,290
accumulated too much resentment,

123
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,290
thus he became Jinwang.

124
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,010
Actually, it's not surprising

125
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,840
that he fell into the demonic path.

126
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,970
I just didn't expect

127
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,800
to meet him here.

128
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,440
Such a powerful guy

129
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,160
is Tu Luohua's subordinate.

130
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,360
How strong must Tu Luohua be?

131
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,340
Are you scared?

132
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,040
Then go back.

133
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,970
Who says I'm scared?

134
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,000
I'm just...

135
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,340
I'm just worried about Feilu.

136
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,200
Ancestor,

137
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,920
I have a question,

138
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,780
I don't know if I should ask

139
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,040
or not.

140
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:08,000
You see, most of the deities in this world

141
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,080
are mostly

142
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:12,880
cultivated from the primordial energy of the beginning of heaven and earth,

143
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,520
the essence of the sun and moon,

144
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,840
or mountains, rivers, and plants.

145
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,200
For example, Nuwa

146
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,930
originated from primal chaos.

147
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:23,960
Queen Mother of the West is related to the spiritual energy of the Kunlun Mountains.

148
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:27,240
Some ancient gods were formed by the essence of the Great Dao.

149
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:27,880
Of course,

150
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:32,410
there are also those who attained enlightenment through later cultivation.

151
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,960
So what opportunity did you get?

152
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,820
cultivated into an immortal.

153
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,400
Yes, I also want to know

154
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,290
what you transformed from.

155
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,560
I'm not a monster.

156
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:51,160
What could I have transformed from?

157
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,900
Since I became conscious,

158
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:55,480
I wandered in the chaos of the three realms.

159
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,240
After attaining enlightenment,

160
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,480
I joined Nuwa's sect

161
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:01,200
and became a minor immortal guarding the Three Mountains Stream.

162
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,200
Nuwa's sect?

163
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:04,380
And a minor immortal? I really...

164
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,560
Brother Qingxuan,

165
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:10,240
what does the immortal realm look like?

166
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,040
If I become an immortal in the future,

167
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:12,960
where will I go?

168
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,480
It's a long story.

169
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,040
Tu Luohua,

170
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,760
now my immortal root is suppressed,

171
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,290
and I don't know her origin.

172
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,580
If I encounter her,

173
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,820
I don't have full confidence either.

174
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,280
In Er City,

175
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,080
with your divine power and murderous intent,

176
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,880
did you look like your immortal root was destroyed?

177
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,340
What does it matter to you?

178
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,640
Then why does Sitian Tower,

179
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,360
knowing there is such a powerful monster,

180
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,080
not send troops to eliminate it?

181
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:50,760
Monsters

182
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,080
are also beings of this world.

183
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,880
A great monster is rarely seen in ten thousand years.

184
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,960
Tu Luohua has already become the Monster King.

185
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,820
Even if the court and Sitian Tower dispatch troops,

186
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,810
to be honest,

187
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,730
even if they manage to take down Tu Luohua,

188
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,960
they would have to pay a heavy price.

189
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,880
By then, the court would be shaken,

190
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,610
and the world would be in chaos.

191
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,840
Which is more important

192
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,570
is clear at a glance.

193
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,610
Can you understand?

194
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:18,840
Never mind.

195
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:21,600
Since we are in the mortal world,

196
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,480
let's follow its ways.

197
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,400
High God.

198
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:41,560
It's you.

199
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,160
You still remember me.

200
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,120
I remember everyone

201
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,480
who ascended from Sanshanliu.

202
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,760
Why are you here?

203
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:51,240
Since my ascension,

204
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,600
I obeyed the mandate of heaven

205
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,330
and was sent to Zhexian Terrace

206
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,560
to manage the banishment of immortals.

207
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,480
I heard you were here,

208
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,260
so I came for a chat.

209
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:02,840
High God.

210
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,700
If you want to persuade me,

211
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,200
don't even start.

212
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:06,840
Not at all.

213
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,040
How could I dare to question

214
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,840
what you have decided?

215
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,040
Going this time,

216
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,660
do you have a destination?

217
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,560
This time,

218
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,620
it's not a normal reincarnation.

219
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,440
There is no path of rebirth.

220
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,900
My origin and destination

221
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,840
are both unknown.

222
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,480
I know a good place.

223
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,480
Would you care to listen?

224
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:33,520
Do you still remember?

225
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,320
Where I come from.

226
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,280
Qingqiu.

227
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:47,960
Ping Jie Qiang Hai.
